  "texts": [
    "After tokenizing the full-text representation of the crash parameters, the fine-tuned Llama3 8B will be asked to identify the crash causation.",
    "Additionally, due to its highly generative capabilities, the LLM will provide an explanation for this causation to support the crash causation classification.",
    "This explanation is essential to identify other significant contributing factors of the crash, highlighting the root causes of crashes at each location.",
    "It also suggests effective countermeasures to improve safety and reduce the number of crashes at each location. 6.",
    "RESULTS AND DISCUSSION"
  ]
}